# Maps commit identities to a canonical author for `git shortlog`,
# `git blame --line-porcelain` and GitHub's contributors graph.
#
# `Canonical Name <canonical@email> <commit@email>` reroutes every
# commit (or co-author trailer) sent from `commit@email` to the
# canonical identity, regardless of the original display name. Catches
# every Claude variant (Opus 4.6, Opus 4.7, Sonnet 4.6, …) without
# enumerating each one.

Vyacheslav Pryimak <vyacheslavpryimak@gmail.com> <noreply@anthropic.com>
